Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.56,0:01:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\fad(480,440)\fs39\bord0.5\3c&H4C49B7&\pos(975,613)\fsp-10}＃０６{\fsp5}    想要遵守的约定
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.74,0:02:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老爹 艾拉暂时拜托给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你打算一个人去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.48,0:02:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还是等等后援吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.10,0:02:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.59,0:02:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这条腿已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.99,0:02:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只能截肢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.16,0:02:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.08,0:02:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不会忘记和你一起工作过的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.27,0:02:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是我不会再和你搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.39,0:03:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}感谢各位协助玛莎的案件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.17,0:03:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然结果变成那样了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.32,0:03:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过没有把一般民众卷入事件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.32,0:03:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可以说是不幸中的万幸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.04,0:03:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此外关于地下回收业者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.22,0:03:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}总公司通知说已和R.Security社合作将其一网打尽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不管怎么说负责这个案件的司和艾拉并没有过错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.50,0:04:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.82,0:04:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.56,0:04:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.84,0:04:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.74,0:04:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你在听吗 司
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.57,0:04:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.20,0:04:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽说不是你们的错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.12,0:04:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但也必须负点责任
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.49,0:04:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以你在艾拉恢复出勤之前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.30,0:04:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}留在事务所待机
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.50,0:04:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.26,0:04:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.41,0:04:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就这样解散
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.70,0:05:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.31,0:05:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}醒来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.68,0:05:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他坚持说要熬夜陪你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.93,0:05:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是个顽固的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.21,0:05:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明天就可以活动了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过你的身体本来就有点毛病
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.28,0:05:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还需要几天时间来调整吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不会再和你搭档
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.09,0:06:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早安 现在几点了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.16,0:06:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还是深夜 要睡的话还是回宿舍比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.54,0:06:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉你没事 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.33,0:06:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}整整昏睡了两天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.10,0:06:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大叔还冲我吼说「维护期间不需要陪护 快出去」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.63,0:06:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}总觉得有点不安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不安？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}万一艾拉你就这样一直醒不过来了怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.48,0:06:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}玛莎和凑太呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.63,0:06:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.99,0:06:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香月小姐他们在做后续处理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.30,0:06:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好像全部由我们处理了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.21,0:06:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.69,0:06:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我什么都做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.27,0:06:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.45,0:06:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.64,0:07:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢你 这样关心我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.24,0:07:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我没事的 真的
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.59,0:07:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.47,0:07:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么 你还能笑得出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.56,0:07:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}听好哦 艾拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.44,0:07:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为现在调整还没有全部完成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.94,0:07:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}下班后不要回宿舍要直接来这边哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.74,0:07:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我会全心全意照顾你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.65,0:07:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.09,0:07:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小艾拉 你没事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.33,0:07:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}维护班说还需要继续调整一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.62,0:07:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.14,0:08:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.34,0:08:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小艾拉 麻烦泡杯茶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.70,0:08:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}总是麻烦你真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.43,0:08:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.75,0:08:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我说司啊 你今天还是陪我去喝一杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.29,0:08:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我会带你去有很多漂亮姐姐的店里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用不用 之前也告诉过你我还未成年
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.10,0:08:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}康孝 不要一大早就说这些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.53,0:08:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}下流下流
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.97,0:08:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}塞克可不要这样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.83,0:08:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.51,0:08:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们课的女同事还是一样不近情理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.97,0:08:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉难不成你看上我了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}下次去约会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.51,0:08:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}错误 我没有在看康孝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.08,0:08:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我脆弱的心刚才受到了深深的伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.91,0:08:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司 就算是安慰我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.44,0:08:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陪我喝一杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.13,0:09:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.14,0:09:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 小艾拉 茶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.80,0:09:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都溢出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.63,0:09:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}文件都…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.66,0:09:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.54,0:09:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对不起
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.34,0:09:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早 艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.44,0:09:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和你分开来上班 总有种奇怪的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.36,0:09:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为最近都是一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.08,0:09:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司你笑起来很好看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}突…突然这是怎么了 吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.35,0:09:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过 谢谢夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉 司对你做了什么奇怪的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.13,0:09:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用担心 我们会站在你这边的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没错 我也听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.15,0:09:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}竟敢欺骗纯情的艾拉拉 不可原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.64,0:10:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\move(640,666,640,710,209,918)}看情况 有必要考虑把他从宿舍赶出去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.43,0:10:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来吧 艾拉拉 尽管说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.58,0:10:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.73,0:10:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.91,0:10:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我 只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.17,0:10:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.07,0:10:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有点在意司
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.24,0:10:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.94,0:10:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呜哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.60,0:10:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}注意到的时候 发现目光一直在追随他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.89,0:10:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明明之前没有这么在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.33,0:10:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}额 这究竟是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.93,0:10:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉拉 这就是所谓的那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.76,0:10:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}叫做恋爱的东西！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.51,0:10:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恋爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.49,0:10:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 是恋爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.07,0:10:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啥 恋爱！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.29,0:10:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}额 应该不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.54,0:10:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果是这样 我会全力支持你的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.71,0:10:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}具体来说 我可以24小时监视小司
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.93,0:10:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}彻底掌握小司的生活状态
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.91,0:10:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}生活状态？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.24,0:10:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我说你啊 这跟跟踪狂差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.52,0:11:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想要了解关于喜欢的人的一切 这是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.08,0:11:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我有经验 所以很了解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.63,0:11:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们明天就开始调查哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.70,0:11:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可不会陪你们
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.73,0:11:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小司到底在看什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.38,0:11:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}应该是我的日记
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.21,0:11:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉拉同意他看了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.65,0:11:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么做这么大胆的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.70,0:11:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他说想了解终端服务课的工作规定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.43,0:11:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是借给他看而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.95,0:11:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看日记是最快的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.75,0:11:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉拉的一切都赤果果的写在日记里了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.09,0:11:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好羡慕啊 我也想看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}应该很无趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.98,0:11:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.12,0:11:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是小司司一边看一边坏笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.57,0:11:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.89,0:11:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要说恶心的话 绘瑠你也…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:11:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雪莉 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.70,0:12:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 总感觉有人在看这边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.79,0:12:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有可能是地下回收业者的残党在谋划恐怖事件
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.40,0:12:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在我们的办公室？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.94,0:12:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果真的会干那种事的话也是瞄着本部大楼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.31,0:12:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雪莉对偷窥的戒备可是很强的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.47,0:12:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你觉得是谁让我变成这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难道…是我？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.04,0:12:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雪莉太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.54,0:12:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雪莉比香月可怕多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.52,0:12:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可不会因为这点小事就放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.99,0:12:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}继续啊 继续
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.96,0:12:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们继续吧 艾拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.36,0:12:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还要继续吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.68,0:12:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可不想再陪你们玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.15,0:12:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最近女儿好像找到男朋友了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.62,0:12:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这不是很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.18,0:12:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才不好呢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.99,0:12:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我来帮你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:12:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的吗 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.04,0:13:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 小心点 那个很重的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.28,0:13:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看来已经晚了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.38,0:13:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}别光是笑 来帮我一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.14,0:13:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂 你们再喝多点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.30,0:13:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我在喝啊 虽然只是果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.26,0:13:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司 我先走一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.51,0:13:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再不走我老婆要发飙了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.93,0:13:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对呢 我知道了 你走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.17,0:13:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉 我会记住的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.03,0:13:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂 连去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.08,0:13:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不知道啊 可能去厕所了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.91,0:13:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}比起这个 香月小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你喝太多了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.34,0:13:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}别给我指指点点的 司
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.81,0:13:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没想到竟然要我陪她一起通宵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.23,0:13:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&H7C6C72&\pos(638,314)}男子浴室
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.71,0:14:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}原来如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.02,0:14:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}竟然在这碰到了 真巧啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.91,0:14:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是小司偶然在那里而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.07,0:14:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的是偶然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.26,0:14:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拜托了雪莉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.82,0:14:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是的 你明明没必要和绘瑠一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.39,0:14:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是她真的有非常努力地帮我想事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.18,0:14:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那么 你在意司的哪个方面呢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.91,0:14:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才刚刚经历过玛莎的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.55,0:14:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不懂司为什么还能保持笑容吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.60,0:14:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}确实那家伙一直都笑嘻嘻的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.98,0:15:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司不会是已经忘记了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.41,0:15:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}人有那种忘记不想记住的东西的能力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.15,0:15:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是我从来没听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.52,0:15:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不知道司现在是什么心情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.46,0:15:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之前我和香月一起去了湊太家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.26,0:15:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}准备和他说明一下玛莎的事故
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.00,0:15:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到那之后发现司也在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.27,0:15:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那家伙明明应该在事务所待命的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.12,0:15:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}却一个人去找湊太道歉
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.45,0:15:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呐 司
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.99,0:15:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}玛莎去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.49,0:15:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我还没能和玛莎好好道别呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.26,0:15:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你跟我说好的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.89,0:15:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要把玛莎带回这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.78,0:16:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对不起 真的对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.55,0:16:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.01,0:16:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么要道歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.59,0:16:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}让我见见玛莎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.76,0:16:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.83,0:16:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之后 他被香月小姐说「不要擅自行动」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.53,0:16:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被狠狠骂了一顿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.53,0:16:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.45,0:16:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他肯定也是没法忘记的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.41,0:16:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想他也不会让自己忘记的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.16,0:16:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那为什么司会笑得出来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.13,0:16:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不知道 到底为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.17,0:16:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大概是因为悲伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}满在温柔的时候真的很温柔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.96,0:16:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等等 艾拉 这话是什么意思
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.19,0:17:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哦 这不是某部的部长吗 真是巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.50,0:17:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.51,0:17:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老板娘 好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.71,0:17:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都到这里了还工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是个无趣的男人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.05,0:17:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}稍微和老板娘说说话怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.58,0:17:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你不是应该对那些喧嚣的店更加有兴趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.29,0:17:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有时会路过这附近而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.99,0:17:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这次的事 找R.Security社来干预的是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是我也有我的办事原则
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.60,0:17:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}原来职位高也不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.92,0:17:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉 今天到此为止 没有什么大问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.27,0:17:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也就是说明天就可以开始工作了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.78,0:17:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 今晚就可以回宿舍了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.02,0:17:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.10,0:17:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.10,0:17:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}别太勉强自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.60,0:17:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}受不了就说受不了就行了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.17,0:18:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明明是我一直在拖大家后腿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.05,0:18:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}回到现场去工作真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.08,0:18:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你不想回归吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.21,0:18:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是可能又会添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.47,0:18:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是不是麻烦不是由你决定的而是司
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.19,0:18:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.16,0:18:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.84,0:18:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.40,0:19:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H8870E7&\3c&HE9EBEC&\fs30\frz25.027\pos(244,416)}甜蜜新婚生活手册
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.01,0:19:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉的剩余时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你有没有从艾拉那里听到些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.30,0:19:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.35,0:19:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.14,0:19:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉因为和你搭档改变了不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.34,0:19:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和同我搭档的时候样子很不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.69,0:19:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.44,0:19:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}毕竟那时消耗非常大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.15,0:19:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那也是因为她暂时休息了一阵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.99,0:19:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}让艾拉有所改变的 毫无疑问是你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.69,0:19:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果是那样的话 我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.97,0:19:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.01,0:20:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉的寿命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.36,0:20:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}仅剩差不多1000小时了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个 1000小时是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.93,0:20:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.57,0:20:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大概一个月多一点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.64,0:20:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一个月…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到那时就要和对其他的吉芙提尔一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.99,0:20:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}必须对艾拉进行回收
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.50,0:20:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我原本没有打算瞒着你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.45,0:20:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是最后就拖到了这时候才说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.36,0:20:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我对此道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.15,0:20:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那么 你打算怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.10,0:20:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是要就这样继续和艾拉搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.69,0:20:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还是要解除与她的搭档关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.75,0:20:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等待新的吉芙提尔分配过来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.40,0:20:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算要继续这样搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:20:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不管怎样 一个月之后你和艾拉的搭档关系都会结束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.73,0:21:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想和艾拉一直搭档到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.60,0:21:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在我无法想象现在和艾拉以外的人搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.33,0:21:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你确定要那样做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.55,0:21:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是的
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.88,0:21:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.08,0:21:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对哦 今天开始你就回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.37,0:21:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要是去接你就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.34,0:21:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.90,0:21:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个…司
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.49,0:21:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.12,0:21:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}欢迎回来 艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.50,0:22:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司也是 欢迎回来
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.91,0:23:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个 司
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.90,0:23:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一会儿是先吃饭 还是先洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.50,0:23:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还是 吃～我～呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.63,0:23:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个 难道是绘瑠小姐教给你的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.30,0:23:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 是从这里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.86,0:23:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H8870E7&\3c&HE9EBEC&\fs30\frz341.217\move(994,709,994,381,0,400)\frx14\fry30}甜蜜新婚生活手册
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.84,0:23:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊～～～
